Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:03.69,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&334061\4c&334061}{\bord3}それが…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&334061\4c&334061}{\bord3}他们留给我的使命
